{"tid":1555569,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 思想改進 ] 運動在6\\7月能夠如日中天，因為攻擊便是最好的防禦","createTime":"2019-09-09T11:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T22:43:23.000Z","uid":286897,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9302814eeeb9c02f5543da0d038b7439ba88b503","tid":1555569,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"如果講連登係一個小型嘅社會的話<br />\n那我相信6\\7月的連登是最受人敬佩最犀利嘅連登<br />\n6月我們有:<br />\n長輩圖攻勢、 人鏈送物資 、 g20全球登報、 地區化抗爭、 諸如此類<br />\n文宣同埋活動之間<br />\n亦都有一段好長嘅時間可以畀人發酵<br />\n好多時候碌連登評論第十幾個post就係 今個下個禮拜有咩活動&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n( 七月廿二三號我就見到有文宣 將軍澳遊行「 將軍出馬 」 活動舉辦在8月4日)<br />\n便是一個很好的例子<br />\n<br />\n八月亦都 唔錯<br />\n但開始先有啲唔夠很倉卒<br />\n文宣同活動差距嘅時間都開始變小咗<br />\n變相少咗時間宣傳<br />\n開始形成咗惡性循環<br />\n( 當初搞香港之路嗰 執行人搞問卷 陣時都覺得有啲倉卒人可能太少)<br />\n到咗荃葵青大遊行嗰陣時文宣都少得明顯咗<br />\n可能活動前五六日先有<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解到咗8月尾9月<br />\n我哋做嘅嘢由做實事spin左去評論上<br />\n班狗官講乜差乜差 fake news <br />\n其實浪費咗我哋嘅時間<br />\n<br />\n我喺度諗緊其實我哋運動嘅目標係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"> 在香港實踐共同嘅理想<br />\n還是比流言蜚語限制行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家值得注意嘅係 fake news 謠傳消息<br />\n至6月以嚟就有啦<br />\n但係點解淨淨係呢個時候發揮作用而非之前<br />\n大家因為發生咩事<br />\n 已可以度過六七月嗰段假新聞時期呢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> 因為我哋冇理到佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我深信呢場運動 最穩陣最有用事情<br />\n就係企出嚟做嘢\\俾suggestion\\ 結識同路人<br />\n評論也是人之常情但這不是最重要的<br />\n記住記住<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong> 行動至上<br />\n評論為輔</strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n聽日繼續<br />\n<br />\n913賀中秋<br />\n914天水圍親子遊<br />\n915民陣遊行"},{"pid":"1befaf6555407372c366241c00053b48148cfcd5","tid":1555569,"uid":196871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:18:33.000Z","msg":"推俾多D人睇到"},{"pid":"0e165e17a325eb3670e3c749db8f2d80797c8b11","tid":1555569,"uid":196871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:18:53.000Z","msg":"推俾多D人睇到"},{"pid":"3221b66e138dd4d3da4786e0c0b2b271e442c8c2","tid":1555569,"uid":196871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:19:06.000Z","msg":"推俾多D人睇到"},{"pid":"42a4ec65635edfddf605a893dde24cf4404f6d22","tid":1555569,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1eaed83b6c503f8e782b94929cd329b12ef4ee","tid":1555569,"uid":252993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:20:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9985a5e3488e99d00a114278c5a78705f50e8e8b","tid":1555569,"uid":168368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3127a2b97bd600df3a38d40eb4dc456601656bb3","tid":1555569,"uid":168368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a7bb2454e3bc4b968f918f8af100763adf12f1","tid":1555569,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3127a2b97bd600df3a38d40eb4dc456601656bb3","tid":1555569,"uid":168368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T22:43:23.000Z","msg":"吹水台好快沉<br />\np牌推唔到"}]}